19f. Exact Form byte-list membrane.
    - Status: landed in `observe/jit-byte-list-membrane.fk`.
    - Witness: `observe/tests/jit-byte-list-membrane-band.fk` returns
      134217727.
    - Scope: exact byte-list preservation and validation before host install.
      It still does not call `fk_nat_install`, `fk_native_call`, or a host
      function pointer.
    - Proves: Form-emitted carrier bytes, checked array/list bytes, checked
      field bytes, checked div bytes, and arbitrary valid Form byte lists are
      admitted only when every byte is in 0..255 and full source, guard, fault,
      deopt, root, ABI, relocation, safepoint, and exception metadata exists;
