20. Full Form-native JIT witnessed.
    - Status: pending.
    - Needs: runtime integration so hot source recipes lower through the
      Form-owned IR/backend bundles/byte streams into the existing host
      install/call membrane, dispatch native, throw source-attributed runtime
      exceptions, deopt/melt safely, and pass the repo's native witness sweep
      without C-lowering as the optimizer source.
